<%= image_tag("SugarbushConditions.png", :alt => "rss fed") %>
<h1>Overview</h1>
<h2>Trail quality</h2>
<p> Sugarbush has a wide array of trails for all types of ski and snowboarders. The main trails such as the ones coming off the express quad are perfect for long winding rides down
  /n There are many winding trails that give the feel of a rollercoaster. Many of these are skiied off past 1 pm. Sugarbush gets enough powder in the more advanced trails after a snowfall.</p>
